description: The FTSE EPRA/NAREIT Developed Europe Ex UK Capped Net Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Listed real estate companies and REITS listed in Developed Europe, ex UK The largest and most liquid companies Weighted by free-float adjusted market capitalisation Quarterly index review Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.ftse.com
